        "management": "Indicated for AV block with normal sinus node or SSS. Maintains AV synchrony. DDD/R mode. More physiologic."
      },
      {
        "id": "crt_pacemaker",
        "name": "Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy (CRT-P/CRT-D)",
